weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 4 V-League g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh, G\u0110KT HAGL Chung Hae Soung \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecf ra kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1ec1 m\u00e0n th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng, H\u1ed3ng Duy.<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u thu\u1ed9c v\u00f2ng 4 <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/vleague-c291-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">V-League 2018</span>, CLB HAGL \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i s\u00edt sao 3-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng t\u00e2n binh Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n. Tuy v\u1eady, ban hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n HAGL v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1ec1 h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 khi h\u1ecd li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp m\u1eafc l\u1ed7i d\u1eabn t\u1edbi nh\u1eefng b\u00e0n g\u1ee1 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u1ea1n.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"GDKT Chung Hae Soung trao doi voi Cong Phuong\" title=\"G\u0110KT Chung Hae Soung trao \u0111\u1ed5i v\u1edbi C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/2/gdkt-hagl-buc-boi-vi-cong-phuong-hong-duy.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>G\u0110KT HAGL b\u1ef1c b\u1ed9i v\u00ec C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng, H\u1ed3ng Duy<span style=\"font-family: arial, verdana, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, helvetica, sans-serif; text-align: start;\">&nbsp;\u0111\u00e1 kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh</span></h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft, sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u G\u0110KT Chung Hae Soung \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecf r\u00f5 s\u1ef1 kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng khi c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 HAGL \u0111\u1ec3 Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh ghi b\u00e0n d\u1ec5, b\u1edfi tuy\u1ebfn tr\u00ean ch\u01a1i h\u1eddi h\u1ee3t \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1ea5t b\u00f3ng, kh\u00f4ng can thi\u1ec7p c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 c\u00e1c pha ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng nhanh.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1ecb \u00f4ng Chung nh\u1eafc nh\u1edf l\u00e0 C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng. Ch\u00e2n s\u00fat x\u1ee9 Ngh\u1ec7 sau khi v\u00e0o s\u00e2n trong hi\u1ec7p 2 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n h\u1ecfng v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng pha \u0111i b\u00f3ng &ldquo;h\u00fac \u0111\u1ea7u v\u00e0o t\u01b0\u1eddng&rdquo;, d\u00f9 xung quanh anh c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u1ed1ng tr\u1ea3i ch\u1ec9 ch\u1edd chuy\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ec3 n\u1edbi r\u1ed9ng c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede b\u00e0n thua th\u1ee9 2, H\u1ed3ng Duy \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1ea5t b\u00f3ng r\u1ea5t nguy hi\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc khu v\u1ef1c c\u1ea5m \u0111\u1ecba d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn b\u00e0n th\u1eafng ch\u1edbp nho\u00e1ng c\u1ee7a ngo\u1ea1i binh Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh. N\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4n kh\u00e9o h\u01a1n, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn b\u00e0n thua th\u1ee9 hai \u1edf nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat b\u00f9 gi\u1edd cu\u1ed1i tr\u1eadn.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngay sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/vleague/gdkt-chung-hae-soung-cong-phuong-phai-thay-doi-291-173999.html\" target=\"_blank\">G\u0110KT Chung Hae Soung</span> c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 bu\u1ed5i n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n trong ph\u00f2ng thay \u0111\u1ed3 v\u1edbi c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7. Nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c c\u0169ng hy v\u1ecdng c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 s\u1ebd thi \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u1eb7t ch\u1ebd h\u01a1n trong nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo m\u00e0 s\u1eafp t\u1edbi l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i tr\u00ean s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch v\u00e0o chi\u1ec1u t\u1ed1i mai 5/4.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nThanh Long (B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h)<br>\r\n<strong><em>Highlight HAGL 3-2 Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh (</em></strong><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:Roboto;mso-fareast-font-family:&#10;&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#081F2C;&#10;mso-fareast-language:KO\"><o:p></o:p></span><strong><em>v\u00f2ng 4 V-League 2018)</em></strong></p>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/4/1/Highlight-HAGL-vs-Nam-Dinh-vong-4-vleague.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"788","checkdouble":"183500"},{"date":"11:00 04/04","title":"C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e9 l\u1ed9 chuy\u1ec7n c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng ra s\u00e2n d\u00f9 g\u1eb7p ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"http://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/3/18/cong-phuong-he-lo-chuyen-co-gang-ra-san-du-gap-chan-thuong.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both