u1ed9i h\u00ecnh thi \u0111\u1ea5u ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1, ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng Park.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tien dao Cong Phuong co gang ra san du gap chan thuong hinh anh\" title=\"Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng ra s\u00e2n d\u00f9 g\u1eb7p ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/18/HAGL-va-nhung-bai-toan-can-tim-loi-giai-o-V-League-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e9 l\u1ed9 chuy\u1ec7n c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng ra s\u00e2n d\u00f9 g\u1eb7p ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea1i <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/vleague-c291-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">V-League </span>n\u0103m nay, ch\u00e2n s\u00fat x\u1ee9 Ngh\u1ec7 c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 quan tr\u1ecdng trong l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 n\u00fai. \u1ede chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a HAGL tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh, C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tung ra s\u00e2n \u1edf nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i tr\u1eadn. Anh \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c d\u00f9 v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 quan tr\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 n\u00fai n\u00ean kh\u00f4ng \u00edt l\u1ea7n C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u00e3 xin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n thi \u0111\u1ea5u d\u00f9 ch\u01b0a b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng. Trong m\u1ed9t chia s\u1ebb m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o qu\u00ea \u0110\u00f4 L\u01b0\u01a1ng, Ngh\u1ec7 An cho hay: \u201cL\u0103n x\u1ea3 l\u1ea5y b\u00f3ng, ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p \u0103n \u00fd c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i, d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m ghi b\u00e0n... l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00e0 Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng lu\u00f4n n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c thi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ecf. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 tr\u00e1i b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7, tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 ph\u1ea3i s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng t\u00e2m l\u00fd c\u00f9ng th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ea7u, v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua nh\u1eefng c\u01a1n \u0111au t\u1eeb ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng. C\u00f3 nh\u1eefng l\u00fac, v\u00ec mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u, s\u00e1t c\u00e1nh b\u00ean \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i m\u00e0 Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng ph\u1ea3i xin Ban hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n \u0111\u00e1 d\u00f9 ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng ch\u01b0a b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n 100%\u201d.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f2n nh\u1edb \u1edf VCK U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 h\u1ed3i th\u00e1ng 1 v\u1eeba qua, C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 c\u0169ng c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng ra s\u00e2n thi \u0111\u1ea5u cho <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/dtqg/hlv-park-hang-seo-len-danh-sach-58-cau-thu-u23-viet-nam-cho-asiad-2018-292-183467.html\" target=\"_blank\">U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam </span>d\u00f9 ch\u01b0a b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ecf t\u1edbi phong \u0111\u1ed9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a anh. Tuy nhi\u00ean s\u1ed1 10 HAGL v\u1eabn thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7y n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c v\u00e0 g\u00f3p c\u00f4ng v\u00e0o chi\u1ebfn t\u00edch gi\u00e0nh ng\u00f4i \u00c1 qu\u00e2n ch\u00e2u l\u1ee5c c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nThanh Long (B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h)<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:\nRoboto;mso-fareast-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";mso-bidi-font-family:\"times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" color:#081f2c;mso-fareast-language:ko\"=\"\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"787","checkdouble":"183501"},{"date":"09:25 04/04","title":"Tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m c\u1ee7a NHM l\u00e0 ca ng\u1ee3i Ronaldo","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"http://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/4/trach-nhiem-cua-nhm-la-ca-ngoi-ronaldo-ghi-ban-truoc-juventus.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContainer video{left:0}.adContainer{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;z-index:2}.jp-video-full div.adContainer div{top:0;left:0}.closeAdsbt{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5;cursor:pointer;border-radius:3px;font-weight:bold}.closeAds{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5}.articlerelatepannel{padding:6px;margin-top:5px;margin-bottom:5px;background-color:#f7f7f7;border:solid 1px #069241}.articlerelate{padding:6px;display:list-item;list-style-type:square;margin-