ont-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u00eam m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n, Cristiano Ronaldo ghi b\u00e0n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Juventus. L\u1ea7n n\u00e0y l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t si\u00eau ph\u1ea9m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea3 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi ca ng\u1ee3i bao g\u1ed3m c\u1ea3 HLV Massimiliano Allegri c\u1ee7a ch\u00ednh \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Italia.</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Ronaldo l\u1eadp si\u00eau ph\u1ea9m</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-chau-au/hlv-juventus-giai-thich-ly-do-tham-bai-truoc-real-184-183485.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>HLV Massimiliano Allegri</strong></span> kh\u00f4ng gi\u1ea5u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 bu\u1ed3n b\u00e3 khi Juventus th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 0-3 ngay tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Real Madrid t\u1ea1i t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i Champions League 2017/18. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u00f4ng cho r\u1eb1ng tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi xem nh\u01b0 \u00f4ng kh\u00f4ng g\u00ec kh\u00e1c ngo\u00e0i ca ng\u1ee3i Cristiano Ronaldo v\u00e0 si\u00eau ph\u1ea9m m\u00e0 anh l\u1eadp \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1eabn bi\u1ebft Real Madrid v\u00e0 Cristiano Ronaldo \u0111ang c\u00f3 phong \u0111\u1ed9 r\u1ea5t cao, c\u0169ng \u00edt ai ng\u1edd h\u1ecd l\u1ea1i b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5 \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1eady tr\u01b0\u1edbc Juventus v\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao trong ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1. Trong khi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Ho\u00e0ng gia T\u00e2y Ban Nha th\u1eafng t\u1edbi 3-0 ngay tr\u00ean kh\u00e1ch, th\u00eam m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n Ronaldo ghi b\u00e0n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Juventus kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 1 m\u00e0 c\u00f2n 2 b\u00e0n y nh\u01b0 chung k\u1ebft Champions League m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Trach nhiem cua NHM la ca ngoi Ronaldo ghi ban truoc Juventus hinh anh\" title=\"Tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m c\u1ee7a NHM l\u00e0 ca ng\u1ee3i Ronaldo ghi b\u00e0n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Juventus h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/4/trach-nhiem-cua-nhm-la-ca-ngoi-ronaldo-ghi-ban-truoc-juventus.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Th\u00eam m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n, Ronaldo ghi b\u00e0n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Juventus</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong \u0111\u00f3, pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng th\u1ee9 2 ph\u00fat 64 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t si\u00eau ph\u1ea9m. \u0110\u00f3n qu\u1ea3 t\u1ea1t c\u1ee7a Dani Carvajal b\u00ean c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i, ng\u01b0\u1eddi 5 l\u1ea7n gi\u00e0nh Qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng v\u00e0ng th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n m\u1ed9t c\u00fa \u201cng\u1ea3 b\u00e0n \u0111\u00e8n\u201d khi\u1ebfn th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n k\u1ef3 c\u1ef1u Gianluigi Buffon \u0111\u1ee9ng nh\u00ecn trong b\u1ea5t l\u1ef1c.</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nAllegri c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i ca ng\u1ee3i CR7</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-chau-au/mot-tay-huy-diet-juventus-sieu-anh-hung-ronaldo-noi-gi-184-183484.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>B\u00e0n th\u1eafng n\u00f3i tr\u00ean c\u1ee7a Ronaldo</strong></span> khi\u1ebfn cho C\u0110V Juventus c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ee9ng d\u1eady v\u1ed7 tay t\u00e1n th\u01b0\u1edfng. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00e1c ph\u00f3ng vi\u00ean, \u0111\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3t HLV Allegri b\u00e0y t\u1ecf s\u1ef1 ng\u01b0\u1ee1ng m\u1ed9 v\u1edbi si\u00eau sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha. \u201cRonaldo \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9 nh\u1ea5t tr\u00ean th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi trong nh\u1eefng n\u0103m g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cC\u00e1c C\u0110V \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tinh th\u1ea7n kh\u00e1ch quan khi Ronaldo ghi b\u00e0n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Juventus. B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u00f2 ch\u01a1i v\u00e0 sau m\u1ed9t kho\u1ea3nh kh\u1eafc nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi n\u00ean hoan ngh\u00eanh. Hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 Real Madrid v\u00e0 Barcelona c\u00f3 Ronaldo v\u00e0 Lionel Messi, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf l\u1edbn.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Juventus vs Real Madrid tr\u00ean trang Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/du-am-juventus-vs-real-khi-messi-moi-qua-nho-be-so-voi-cr7-184-183488.html\">D\u01b0 \u00e2m Juventus vs Real: Khi \u201cMessi m\u1edbi\u201d qu\u00e1 nh\u1ecf b\u00e9 so v\u1edbi CR7</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/choi-xuat-sac-da-danh-real-madrid-con-duoc-trong-tai-uu-ai-184-183487.html\">Ch\u01a1i xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e0nh, Real Madrid c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i \u01b0u \u00e1i</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/hlv-juventus-giai-thich-ly-do-tham-bai-truoc-real-184-183485.html\">HLV Juventus gi\u1ea3i th\u00edch l\u00fd do th\u1ea3m b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Real</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/nhung-diem-nhan-trong-tran-dai-chien-mot-chieu-juve-vs-real-184-183478.html\">Nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn m\u1ed9t chi\u1ec1u Juventu