in'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Pep Guardiola ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn Liverpool vs Man City r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng ch\u01a1i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng \u00e1p \u0111\u1ea3o ngay tr\u00ean s\u00e2n \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u1edf tr\u1eadn t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft Champions League s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Pep Guardiola phat bieu truoc tran Liverpool vs Man City hinh anh\" title=\"Pep Guardiola ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn Liverpool vs Man City h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/4/pep-guardiola-khang-dinh-se-choi-tan-cong-tai-liverpool.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Pep Guardiola ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn Liverpool vs Man City</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5 c\u1ee7a Man City \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u l\u1eddi khen \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m nay. V\u1edbi phong c\u00e1ch thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u00e1p \u0111\u1ea3o, The Citizens \u0111ang ti\u1ebfn g\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ebfn ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch khi m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eabn c\u00f2n h\u01a1n 1 th\u00e1ng n\u1eefa m\u1edbi k\u1ebft th\u00fac.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nH\u1ecd m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 thua \u0111\u00fang 1 tr\u1eadn t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Liverpool. V\u00e0o \u0111\u00eam nay, \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Pep Guardiola s\u1ebd h\u00e0nh qu\u00e2n \u0111\u1ebfn Anfield m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa. V\u00e0 nhi\u1ec1u chuy\u00ean gia cho r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m m\u00e0 Man City n\u00ean s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt an to\u00e0n h\u01a1n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nHLV Pep Guardiola ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-chau-au/liverpool-vs-man-city-1h45-ngay-54-ai-moi-la-vua-nuoc-anh-184-183490.html\" target=\"_blank\">Liverpool vs Man City</span> r\u1eb1ng: \u201cT\u00f4i bi\u1ebft c\u00e1ch ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng bi\u1ebfn m\u00ecnh th\u00e0nh mi\u1ebfng m\u1ed3i ngon cho Liverpool. B\u1edfi v\u00ec h\u1ecd l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng kho\u1ea3ng tr\u1ed1ng r\u1ea5t xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc. V\u1edbi b\u1ed9 ba t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng l\u00e0 Mane, Salah v\u00e0 Firmino, Liverpool c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u1ee7y di\u1ec7t m\u1ecdi h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1. Nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 c\u00e1ch t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u1edf c\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Liverpool l\u00e0 ch\u01a1i \u0111\u00fang nh\u01b0 phong c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e3 mang ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cN\u1ebfu t\u00f4i n\u00f3i r\u1eb1ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1c v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a, c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 s\u1ebd nh\u00ecn t\u00f4i v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1: \u2018G\u00e3 n\u00e0y s\u1ee3 r\u1ed3i. H\u1eafn kh\u00f4ng tin t\u01b0\u1edfng v\u00e0o kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang ta\u2019. V\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t sai l\u1ea7m l\u1edbn c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i\u201d.<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/liverpool-vs-man-city-1h45-ngay-54-ai-moi-la-vua-nuoc-anh-184-183490.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/4/liverpool-vs-man-city-1h45-ngay-54-ai-moi-la-vua-nuoc-anh.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/liverpool-vs-man-city-1h45-ngay-54-ai-moi-la-vua-nuoc-anh-184-183490.html\">Liverpool vs Man City (1h45 ng\u00e0y 5/4): Ai m\u1edbi l\u00e0 vua n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh?</span><br>\r\n<span>T\u1eeb v\u1ecb th\u1ebf \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7 binh h\u00f9ng t\u01b0\u1edbng m\u1ea1nh b\u01b0\u1edbc qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng, gi\u1edd th\u00ec Premier League ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t nh\u01b0ng c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 duy nh\u1ea5t m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t \u1edf b\u00e1n k\u1ebft...</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng l\u00fd do c\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u00f4ng ch\u1edd l\u00e0 b\u1edfi l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng r\u1ef1c l\u1eeda c\u1ee7a c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i. V\u00e0 HLV Pep Guardiola kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 h\u00f2a 0-0 nh\u1ea1t nh\u1ebdo \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cC\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec1u s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng \u00e1p \u0111\u1eb7t l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh l\u00ean \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n nh\u1ea5t \u1edf Premier League m\u00f9a n\u00e0y. V\u00e0 t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Klopp \u0111\u1ec1u t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 v\u00e0 ch\u01a1i c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn h\u1ebft m\u1ee9c c\u00f3 th\u1ec3. H\u1ecd s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 t\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean l\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u0169ng th\u1ebf. T\u00f4i cam \u0111oan r\u1eb1ng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ng\u00e0y mai s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t th\u00fa v\u1ecb\u201d.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (Bongda24h)</strong></div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"784","checkdouble":"183499"},{"date":"11:23 04/04","title":"G\u00f3c nh\u00ecn: Ronaldo h\u00f3a \u201cTh\u00e1nh\u201d, ng\u01b0\u1eddi kh\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 Messi","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"http://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/4/ronaldo-toa-sang-tran-dau-juventus-vs-real-madrid-va-su-kho-chiu-cua-messi.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContainer video{left:0}.adContainer{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;z-index:2}.jp-video-full div.adContainer div{top:0;left:0}.closeAdsbt{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5;cursor:pointer;border-radius:3px;font-weight:bold}.closeAds{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5}.articlerelatepannel{padding:6px;margin-top:5px;margin-bottom:5px;background-color:#f7f7f7;border:solid 1px #069241}.articlerelate{padding:6px;display:list-item;list-style-type:square;margin-left:1.2em;border-bottom:dashed 1px #888}.articlerelate:last-child{border-bottom:0}div.articlerelate>a{color:#000;text-decoration:none;font-size:13px;font-weight:bold}div.articlerelate>a:hover{color:#f00;text-decoration:none;font-size:13px;font-weight:bold}.articlerelate2{padding:6px;min-height:72px}div.articlerelate2>a{color:#000;text-decoration:none;font-size:13px;font-weight:bold}div.articlerel