00f4n. Nh\u01b0ng n\u1ebfu ph\u1ea3i t\u00ecm ra m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y b\u1ee9c b\u1ed1i nh\u1ea5t trong m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n si\u00eau \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ee7a si\u00eau sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3, \u0111\u00f3 h\u1eb3n ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea1i k\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ecbch Lionel Messi c\u1ee7a anh.</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e3 xem l\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i th\u1ed5n th\u1ee9c v\u00ec Ronaldo</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-chau-au/trach-nhiem-cua-nhm-la-ca-ngoi-ronaldo-ghi-ban-truoc-juventus-184-183493.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>\u0110\u1ebfn ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 Juventus</strong></span> c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ee9ng d\u1eady v\u1ed7 tay t\u00e1n th\u01b0\u1edfng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Cristiano Ronaldo trong tr\u1eadn t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i Champions League. Kh\u00f4ng nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u00ean th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c may m\u1eafn \u0111\u00f3 v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c r\u1ea5t hi\u1ebfm t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n n\u00e0o xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc \u0111\u1ebfn \u00e1m \u1ea3nh nh\u01b0 v\u1eady.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u00eam m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n, Ronaldo t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Juventus vs Real Madrid. Sau c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap t\u1ea1i Cardiff chung k\u1ebft Champions League m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap n\u1eefa t\u1ea1i Turin t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u. Kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd n\u1ebfu sau tr\u1eadn Ronaldo g\u1ecdi m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c \u0111i\u1ec7n tho\u1ea1i an \u1ee7i \u0111\u00e0n anh Gianluigi Buffon.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Goc nhin ve Ronaldo toa sang tran dau Juventus vs Real Madrid hinh anh\" title=\"G\u00f3c nh\u00ecn v\u1ec1 Ronaldo t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Juventus vs Real Madrid h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/4/Goc-nhin-ve-Ronaldo-toa-sang-tran-dau-Juventus-vs-Real-Madrid-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Ronaldo l\u00fac n\u00e0y l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ng\u0103n c\u1ea3n</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nCh\u01b0a \u0111\u1ea7y 1 n\u0103m, Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m tung l\u01b0\u1edbi m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n v\u0129 \u0111\u1ea1i nh\u1ea5t l\u1ecbch s\u1eed b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1edbi 4 l\u1ea7n ch\u1ec9 sau 2 l\u1ea7n ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n. \u01af\u1edbc m\u01a1 c\u1ee7a Buffon l\u00e0 th\u00eam m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n \u0111\u0103ng quang t\u1ea1i Champions League tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi gi\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec7. Nh\u01b0ng g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 n\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 tan bi\u1ebfn sau khi b\u1ecb CR7 ph\u00e1 l\u01b0\u1edbi li\u00ean t\u1ee5c v\u00e0 ph\u00e1 lu\u00f4n hy v\u1ecdng \u0111i ti\u1ebfp c\u1ee7a Juventus.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 0-3 \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u00fa s\u1ed1c c\u1ef1c l\u1edbn v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi Juventus. \u0110\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1eb7t h\u01a1n 1 ch\u00e2n v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft Champions League. Nh\u01b0ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi Juve kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u1eadn <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-chau-au/du-am-juventus-03-real-madrid-gioi-han-nao-cho-ken-ken-trang-184-183492.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Real v\u00e0 Ronaldo</strong></span>. H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 v\u00e0 \u0111ang l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u00f4ng Vua t\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u \u00c2u, nh\u1eefng t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 v\u00e0 c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chinh ph\u1ee5c b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 th\u1eed th\u00e1ch n\u00e0o d\u00f9 l\u00e0 kh\u1eafc nghi\u1ec7t nh\u1ea5t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Goc nhin Ronaldo hoa Thanh, nguoi kho chiu nhat la Messi hinh anh 2\" title=\"G\u00f3c nh\u00ecn Ronaldo h\u00f3a Th\u00e1nh, ng\u01b0\u1eddi kh\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 Messi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/4/Goc-nhin-Ronaldo-hoa-Thanh,-nguoi-kho-chiu-nhat-la-Messi-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Th\u00eam m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n anh gieo s\u1ea7u cho Juventus v\u00e0 Buffon</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nRonaldo \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u1ea3n. Anh l\u00e0 bi\u1ec3u t\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng r\u1ef1c r\u1ee1 m\u1ed9t th\u1eadp k\u1ef7 qua c\u1ee7a Real. C\u0169ng ch\u00ednh CR7 th\u00eam m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n t\u1ea1o n\u00ean kho\u1ea3nh kh\u1eafc ti\u00eau bi\u1ec3u cho anh v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh t\u1ea1i tr\u1eddi \u00c2u. Ph\u00fat 64, nh\u1eadn qu\u1ea3 t\u1ea1t c\u1ee7a Dani Carvajal, s\u1ed1 7 c\u1ee7a Real tung ng\u01b0\u1eddi &ldquo;ng\u1ea3 b\u00e0n \u0111\u00e8n&rdquo; ngo\u1ea1n m\u1ee5c khi\u1ebfn Buffon c\u00f9ng c\u1ea3 h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 Juventus ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y b\u1ea5t l\u1ef1c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u00ean kh\u00e1n \u0111\u00e0i, c\u00e1c C\u0110V \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 d\u00f9 n\u00e9t m\u1eb7t ch\u1eb3ng vui v\u1ebb g\u00ec c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ee9ng b\u1eadt d\u1eady d\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng tr\u00e0ng v\u1ed7 tay th\u00e1n ph\u1ee5c cho Ronaldo. B\u00ean ngo\u00e0i s\u00e2n, HLV Zidane \u00f4m \u0111\u1ea7u kh\u00f4ng hi\u1ec3u chuy\u1ec7n g\u00ec \u0111ang x\u1ea3y ra. C\u0169ng c\u00f3 v\u00f4 s\u1ed1 kh\u00e1n gi\u1ea3 truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh m\u1edf r\u1ed9ng m\u1ecdi gi\u00e1c quan \u0111\u00f3n nh\u1eadn tuy\u1ec7t ph\u1ea9m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ea1o ra t\u1eeb \u0111\u00f4i ch\u00e2n c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi 5 l\u1ea7n gi\u00e0nh Qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng v\u00e0ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNgay c\u1ea3 b\u00e0n m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 ch\u1ec9 sau 2 ph\u00fat 47 gi\u00e2y c\u1ee7a Ronaldo c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n. N\u00f3 ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf v\u00e0o th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ec9nh cao phong \u0111\u1ed9, Real v\u00e0 Ronaldo ch\u1eb3ng c\u00f3 gi\u1edbi h\u1ea1n n\u00e0o. C\u1ea3 ch\u00e2u \u00c2u ng\u1ea3 m\u0169 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Los Blancos d\u00f9 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd c\u00f3 ph\u1ea7n lo l\u1eafng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"CDV Juve va Zidane\" title=\"CDV Juve va Zidane\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/4/CDV-Juve-va-Zidane.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Ronaldo t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Juventus vs Real Madrid khi\u1ebfn nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u00e1n ph\u1ee5c</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\n<br>\r\nMessi \u0111ang kh\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu h\u01a1n ai h\u1ebft</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nBongda24h.vn ph\u1ea3i nh\u1ea5n m\u1ea1nh ngay: Lionel Messi kh\u00f4ng ghen t\u1ecb khi <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-chau-au/nhung-thong-ke-gay-soc-ve-ronaldo-o-tran-dau-voi-juventus-184-183475.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Ronaldo t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Juventus vs Real Madrid</strong></span>. Messi c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t si\u00eau sao, c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 ng\u1ea5t ng\u00e2y v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 khi\u1ebfp s\u1ee3 nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n. Nh\u01b0ng m\u1ea5u ch\u1ed1t n\u1eb1m \u1edf ph\u1ea7n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Real Madrid nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 ch\u00fang ta \u0111\u1ec1u ph\u1ea3i c\u00f4ng nh\u1eadn m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u: Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 Ronaldo, to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean kh\u00e1c c\u1ee7a Real c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t tr\u01b0\u1edbc Juventus. CR7 l\u00e0 ng\u00f4i sao s\u00e1ng nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i th\u00e0nh Turin \u0111\u00eam th\u1ee9 3, song nh\u1eefng v\u1ec7 tinh xung quanh anh kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 m\u1edd nh\u1ea1t ch\u00fat n\u00e0o.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"tap the Real khong tam thuong\" title=\"tap the Real khong tam thuong\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/4/tap-the-Real-khong-tam-thuong.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">T\u1eadp th\u1ec3 Real l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng t\u1ea7m th\u01b0\u1eddng</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nH\u1ecd chung tay gi\u00fap Real l\u1ea5n l\u01b0\u1edbt Juventus ngay tr\u00ean s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch. D\u00f9 \u1edf th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 n\u00e0o, t\u1eeb ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t b\u00f3ng (55,6% so v\u1edbi 44,4%), d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m (14-12) hay tr\u00fang \u0111\u00edch (5-2)&hellip;, Los Blancos c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ec1u chi\u1ebfm th\u1ebf th\u01b0\u1ee3ng phong. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nRonaldo \u0111\u00e3 l\u1eadp c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap c\u00f9ng 1 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o, song ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea3m \u01a1n Isco v\u00e0 Carvajal v\u1edbi 2 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ea7y th\u00f4ng minh. Anh c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea3m \u01a1n Marcelo, ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1ea1n th\u00e2n ngo\u00e0i \u0111\u1eddi v\u00e0 c\u0169ng c\u1ef1c hi\u1ec3u \u00fd m\u00ecnh tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ecf. 2 ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1eadt t\u01b0\u1eddng c\u00f9ng nhau tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Brazil v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua c\u1ea3 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Buffon r\u1ed3i \u1ea5n \u0111\u1ecbnh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 3-0 cho Real.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMessi \u1ea5m \u1ee9c l\u00e0 \u1edf ch\u1ed7 \u0111\u00f3. D\u0129 nhi\u00ean Leo ch\u1eb3ng ng\u1ea1i g\u00ec n\u00f3i ra \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 g\u00e2y m\u1ea5t \u0111o\u00e0n k\u1ebft n\u1ed9i b\u1ed9 Barca. Nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i, b\u1ea1n, ch\u00fang ta \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 nh\u00ecn ra s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t r\u00f5 r\u1ec7t c\u1ee7a hai g\u00e3 kh\u1ed5ng l\u1ed3 T\u00e2y Ban Nha. Barca = si\u00eau sao Messi + 10 t\u1ea7m th\u01b0\u1eddng c\u00f2n Real = si\u00eau sao Ronaldo + 10 ng\u00f4i sao.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ronaldo toa sang truoc Juventus va su ghen ti Messi\" title=\"Ronaldo toa sang truoc Juventus va su ghen ti Messi\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/4/ronaldo-toa-sang-tran-dau-juventus-vs-real-madrid-va-su-kho-chiu-cua-messi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Messi kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c may m\u1eafn nh\u01b0 Ronaldo</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1ea1i Barca, s\u1ef1 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 d\u00e0nh cho Messi kh\u00f4ng nhi\u1ec1u nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00e0ng gi\u1ea3m s\u00fat theo th\u1eddi gian. D\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Pep Guardiola v\u00e0 Luis Enrique, El Pulga g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c mi\u1ec5n nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1. T\u1edbi khi Ernesto Valverde l\u00ean n\u1eafm quy\u1ec1n, m\u1ed3 h\u00f4i v\u00e0 m\u00e1u c\u1ee7a Messi \u0111\u1ed5 ra tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nN\u1ebfu Messi kh\u00f4ng tham gia tranh c\u01b0\u1edbp b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 l\u00f9i s\u00e2u t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c, ch\u1eb3ng ai l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u00f3. Ph\u1ea7n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9 c\u00f3 h\u1ea1n \u0111\u00f4i khi ch\u1ec9 bi\u1ebft co v\u1ec1 th\u1eadt g\u1ea7n khung th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 v\u00e0 ph\u00f3 th\u00e1c to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 t\u1eeb v\u1ea1ch v\u00f4i gi\u1eefa s\u00e2n \u0111\u1ed5 sang b\u00ean kia cho s\u1ed1 10 huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a CLB.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/barca-vuot-qua-chelsea-ban-len-xac-chet-co-gi-dang-tung-ho-184-182176.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/15/barca-vuot-qua-chelsea-ban-len-xac-chet-co-gi-dang-tung-ho.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/barca-vuot-qua-chelsea-ban-len-xac-chet-co-gi-dang-tung-ho-184-182176.html\">Barca v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Chelsea: B\u1eafn l\u00ean &ldquo;x\u00e1c ch\u1ebft&rdquo;, c\u00f3 g\u00ec \u0111\u00e1ng tung h\u00f4?</span><br>\r\n<span>H\u00e3y ca ng\u1ee3i Messi h\u1ebft m\u1ee9c c\u00f3 th\u1ec3, nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1eebng l\u00e0m \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 v\u1edbi Barca v\u00e0 HLV Valverde. Chelsea qu\u00e1 t\u1ec7 v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec qu\u00e1 gh\u00ea g\u1edbm.</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00e1i c\u00e1ch m\u00e0 Real v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Juventus ph\u1ea3i n\u00f3i l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng t\u1ef3 v\u1ebft. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u Roma t\u1ea1i t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i r\u1ea1ng s\u00e1ng mai (5/4), tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Barca l\u00e0 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Chelsea. C\u00f9ng l\u00e0 c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t 3-0 nh\u01b0ng c\u00e1i c\u00e1ch m\u00e0 g\u00e3 kh\u1ed5ng l\u1ed3 x\u1ee9 Catalonia th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n th\u00ec ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n kh\u00e1c Real.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nReal th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n v\u1ecb th\u1ebf b\u1ec1 tr\u00ean, l\u1ea5n l\u01b0\u1edbt Juventus tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi ph\u01b0\u01a1ng di\u1ec7n v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n ghi th\u00eam b\u00e0n ngay c\u1ea3 khi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 l\u00e0 3-0. Ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, Barca t\u1ef1 h\u1ea1 m\u00ecnh, nh\u01b0\u1eddng th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn cho Chelsea v\u00e0 l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c co v\u1ec1 ngay sau khi khai th\u00f4ng th\u1ebf b\u1ebf t\u1eafc (do c\u00f4ng Messi). T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t k\u1ec3 tr\u00ean l\u00e0 m\u1ea5u ch\u1ed1t g\u00e2y ra s\u1ef1 kh\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu cho Messi v\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi Ronaldo.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>\u0110\u1ed8I H\u00ccNH THI \u0110\u1ea4U<br>\r\nJuventus:</strong> Buffon; De Sciglio, Barzagli, Chiellini, Asamoah (Mandzukic 69'); Khedira (Cuadrado 75'), Bentancur; Douglas Costa (Matuidi 69'), Dybala, Sandro; Higuain.<br>\r\n<strong>Real Madrid:</strong> Navas; Carvajal, Ramos, Varane, Marcelo; Kroos, Casemiro, Isco (Asensio 75'), Modric (Kovacic 82'); Ronaldo, Benzema (Vazquez 59').<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td s