:5px;background:#000 url(images/ui-bg_flat_10_000000_40x100.png) 50% 50% repeat-x;opacity:.2;filter:Alpha(Opacity=20);border-radius:5px}.link-web>a{color:#555;font-size:12px;line-height:24px}body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 18px;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1ed9t ngu\u1ed3n tin t\u1eeb M\u1ef9 ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 Zlatan Ibrahimovic \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i m\u1ed9t l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb c\u1ea3 tr\u0103m tri\u1ec7u USD t\u1eeb Trung Qu\u1ed1c. Sau khi r\u1eddi Man United v\u00e0 Ibrahimovic kh\u00f4ng sang Trung Qu\u1ed1c, anh quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u1ecdn M\u1ef9 v\u00e0 LA Galaxy l\u00e0 b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 ti\u1ebfp theo.</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong><br>\r\nIbrahimovic r\u1eddi M.U t\u1edbi LA Galaxy<br>\r\n</strong><br>\r\nTheo t\u1ea1p ch\u00ed Sports Illustrated, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/tin-tuc-world-cup/ibrahimovic-len-tieng-ve-kha-nang-du-world-cup-2018-439-182718.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Zlatan Ibrahimovic</strong></span> \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 100 tri\u1ec7u USD t\u1eeb Trung Qu\u1ed1c. Thay v\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3, ch\u00e2n s\u00fat 36 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ecdn LA Galaxy t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i Nh\u00e0 ngh\u1ec1 M\u1ef9 MLS l\u00e0m b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nIbrahimovic k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 1 n\u0103m v\u1edbi Manchester United h\u1ed3i \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a 2017/18. Ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng t\u1eeb ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ea7u g\u1ed1i nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o cao k\u1ec1u n\u00e0y nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn. Anh kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p nhi\u1ec1u cho Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch n\u00e0y v\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 v\u1ecfn v\u1eb9n 7 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng v\u00e0 5 t\u1ea1i Premier League, ghi 1 b\u00e0n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ibrahimovic khong sang Trung Quoc va toi LA Galaxy hinh anh\" title=\"Ibrahimovic kh\u00f4ng sang Trung Qu\u1ed1c v\u00e0 t\u1edbi LA Galaxy h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/4/Ibrahimovic-khong-sang-Trung-Quoc-va-toi-LA-Galaxy-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Ibrahimovic kh\u00f4ng sang Trung Qu\u1ed1c m\u00e0 t\u1edbi M\u1ef9</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00e0o th\u00e1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc, Ibrahimovic v\u00e0 M.U \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn ch\u1ea5m d\u1ee9t h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng. Kh\u00f4ng l\u00e2u sau, anh ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c kho\u00e1c l\u00ean m\u00ecnh chi\u1ebfc \u00e1o m\u1edbi t\u1ea1i LA Galaxy. Ibra gia nh\u1eadp \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i Nh\u00e0 ngh\u1ec1 M\u1ef9 MLS theo h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 2 n\u0103m v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eadn m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng 1,5 tri\u1ec7u USD/ n\u0103m.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Ibrahimovic kh\u00f4ng sang Trung Qu\u1ed1c</strong><br>\r\n<br>\r\nJovan Kirovski, gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt c\u1ee7a LA Galaxy m\u1edbi ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 m\u1ed9t th\u00f4ng tin b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd: Ibrahimovic kh\u00f4ng sang Trung Qu\u1ed1c d\u00f9 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1eddi m\u1eddi h\u1eadu h\u0129nh. Ngay c\u1ea3 khi ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ea7u g\u1ed1i c\u1ee7a c\u1ef1u tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n c\u00f2n l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t d\u1ea5u h\u1ecfi, \u0111\u1ea1i gia t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1ef7 d\u00e2n v\u1eabn quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh tr\u1ea3 t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 100 tri\u1ec7u USD trong su\u1ed1t h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng cho anh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nR\u1ed1t c\u1ee5c, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-chau-au/chinh-thuc-ibrahimovic-xac-nhan-tuong-lai-184-182705.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Ibrahimovic \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn LA Galaxy</strong></span> thay v\u00ec phi\u00eau l\u01b0u t\u1ea1i ph\u00eda \u0110\u00f4ng. Kirovski cho bi\u1ebft c\u00f4ng \u0111o\u1ea1n kh\u00f3 nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn n\u00e0y l\u00e0 gi\u1ea3i th\u00edch cho \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Ibra, Mino Raiola r\u1eb1ng t\u1ea1i sao ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng 1,5 tri\u1ec7u USD/ n\u0103m.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng r\u1ed1t c\u1ee5c v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 nghi\u00eam t\u00fac c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh c\u1ed9ng th\u00eam vi\u1ec7c Ibrahimovic kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 ch\u00fa tr\u1ecdng ti\u1ec1n b\u1ea1c trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n n\u00e0y c\u1ee7a s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p, LA Galaxy \u0111\u00e3 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng. \u0110\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd, h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng ph\u1ee5 n\u00e0o t\u1eeb c\u00e1c nh\u00e0 t\u00e0i tr\u1ee3 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m th\u1ecfa m\u00e3n nh\u1eefng y\u00eau c\u1ea7u t\u1eeb c\u1ef1u ng\u00f4i sao M.U.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 Zlatan Ibrahimovic tr\u00ean trang Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/tin-bong-da/nong-sieu-ibra-ra-mat-mls-bang-tuyet-tac-volley-tam-xa-279-183289.html\">N\u00d3NG: Si\u