/ui-bg_diagonals-thick_20_666666_40x40.png) 50% 50% repeat;opacity:.5;filter:Alpha(Opacity=50)}.ui-widget-shadow{margin:-5px 0 0 -5px;padding:5px;background:#000 url(images/ui-bg_flat_10_000000_40x100.png) 50% 50% repeat-x;opacity:.2;filter:Alpha(Opacity=20);border-radius:5px}.link-web>a{color:#555;font-size:12px;line-height:24px}body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 18px;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Sergio Aguero ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng tham d\u1ef1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Liverpool tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Anfield, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Pep Guardiola ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9.</strong></h2>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</h2>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Aguero d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng kh\u00e1 nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sergio Aguero \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng ra s\u00e2n k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng 1-0 c\u1ee7a Man City tr\u01b0\u1edbc Chelsea v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ea7u th\u00e1ng 3. Ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1988 b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 hai tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu c\u1ee7a Argentina v\u1edbi Italia v\u00e0 T\u00e2y Ban Nha.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Sergio Aguero chan thuong lo tran Liverpool vs Man City hinh anh\" title=\"Sergio Aguero ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng l\u1ee1 tr\u1eadn Liverpool vs Man City h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/26/Sergio-Aguero-chan-thuong-lo-tran-Liverpool-vs-Man-City-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Sergio Aguero ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ea7u g\u1ed1i</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nC\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 30 tu\u1ed5i c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng tham d\u1ef1 hai tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Man City v\u1edbi Stoke City v\u00e0 Everton.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSergio Aguero ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ea7u g\u1ed1i, nh\u1eefng t\u01b0\u1edfng anh s\u1ebd <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/pep-noi-ve-kha-nang-aguero-ra-san-truoc-everton-172-183211.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Everton </strong></span>cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i, nh\u01b0ng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 \u0111ang di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn ph\u1ee9c t\u1ea1p v\u00e0 El Kun ph\u1ea3i r\u1eddi th\u1eddi gian tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i s\u00e2n c\u1ecf.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nVi\u1ec7c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 t\u00ean trong danh s\u00e1ch thi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1edbc Everton khi\u1ebfn NHM Man City lo l\u1eafng, h\u1ecd s\u1ee3 r\u1eb1ng El Kun s\u1ebd b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 chuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Anfield c\u1ee7a <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/clubs/liverpool-2.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Liverpool </strong></span>trong khu\u00f4n kh\u1ed5 l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft Champions League.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Pep th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o v\u1ec1 ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a Aguero</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sergio Aguero ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng tham d\u1ef1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Liverpool tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Anfield, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Pep Guardiola ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u201cC\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd \u1edf l\u1ea1i Manchester, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i t\u1edbi Anfield. Aguero kh\u00f4ng kh\u1ecfe, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ec3 ra s\u00e2n tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 m\u1ea1o hi\u1ec3m v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Aguero\" title=\"Aguero\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/12/Pep-Guardiola-noi-ve-viec-Sergio-Aguero-chan-thuong-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Aguero l\u1ee1 tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft C1 v\u1edbi Liverpool</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft Aguero c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tham d\u1ef1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi MU hay kh\u00f4ng. C\u00e1c b\u00e1c s\u1ef9 n\u00f3i c\u1eadu \u1ea5y t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n nhi\u1ec1u, nh\u01b0ng b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n c\u1eadu \u1ea5y kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u00ecnh kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i, t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng mang theo c\u1eadu \u1ea5y t\u1edbi Anfield\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Aguero kh\u00f4ng ra s\u00e2n tr\u00ean Anfield, tr\u1eadn <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-chau-au/liverpool-vs-man-city-1h45-ngay-54-ai-moi-la-vua-nuoc-anh-184-183490.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Liverpool vs Man City</strong></span> nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Gabriel Jesus l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i sau ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Everton t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 32 Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh, Jesus ghi 1 b\u00e0n gi\u00fap Man City gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 3-1. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1997 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 li\u00ean k\u1ebft v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n Aguero, b\u1edfi v\u1eady s\u1ef1 v\u1eafng m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a El Kun ch\u01b0a ch\u1eafc l\u00e0 th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda v\u1edbi Man xanh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<strong>Phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Aguero \u1edf Premier League 2017/18</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://sja.sportradar.com/w/Bongda24H/17094-40942/033100\">Phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Aguero \u1edf Premier League 2017/18</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (B\u00f3ng \u0110\u00e1 24h)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"780","checkdouble":"183509"},{"date":"22:46 03/04","title":"Ai l\u00e0 nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch V-League 2018 trong m\u1eaft chuy\u00ean gia Vi\u1ec7t?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"http://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/3/17/ai-la-nha-vo-dich-vleague-2018-trong-mat-chuyen-gia-viet.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-fam